  "texts": [
    "From an input video Vin: (i) chunk task-relevant spans for curation and generate task instructions (Sec.",
    "3.1); (ii) estimate camera pose and depth, select a reference image and track 3D points to form a raw trace (Sec.",
    "3.2); (iii) apply world-to-camera alignment (Sec.",
    "3.3); (iv) speed retargeting to produce the final 3D trace (Sec. 3.4).",
    "Figure 5.5Figure 5."
